\id 2TH - Ampeele NT [apz] -Papua New Guinea 1988 (web version -2012 bd)
\h 2 Tesolounika
\toc1 Olo Iyoswo T…®finjo loso Poul AÍûåamu Tesolounika somneÍûåno Mt…®Íûåmokumentisofoho.
